UPCOMING ARTIST SPOTLIGHTS🔦(JAN 2026)

Here is the twice-a-week (posted Sunday & Wednesday) updated lineup of well known (& not as well known) music makers we plan to showcase over the next 6 months. This is not a complete list. These 4 to 5 track spotlights will continue to feature hits & 'hidden gems' from a diverse & eclectic mix of immortals, living legends, little-known performers, pop culture icons, bands/groups, standout vocalists🧑‍🎤and instrumentalists 🎸🎹🎷🎺🥁. 

Genres highlighted include Pop, Jazz, Easy Listening, Funk, ‘Old Skool' R&B & Bossa Nova among other idioms. We also 'shine a light' on notable producers, arrangers & studio musicians whose contributions sometime go unnoticed and under-appreciated. Several artists are featured on their date of birth🎂and/or passing anniversary🕊️.

